Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill allows users to take a simple, four question yes or no quiz, to help them better understand the “occasional constipation” symptoms they may be experiencing; belly pain, discomfort and bloating again and again. 

This skill does not collect or store any personal information and you may exit at any time. This skill is intended to help support a conversation with your health care provider. It does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. 

Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
